<p>
    The Style Guide integration provides an easy way for integration developers to see the pre-defined CSS classes that can be used to style their integrations.
</p>
<h1>Section Headers</h1>
<p>
    Section Headers should be styled using the <span class="class">p-title</span> class.
</p>

