<h1>Links</h1>
<p>
    External links (links that will open in an external browser) should be styled using the <span
        class="class">p-link</span> class. Note that external links are styled the same throughout the Polarity
    application. Integration developers are encouraged to follow the defined link style so users know what behavior to
    expect when they see text styled as a link. Links are styled in blue.
</p>

